data.description: **Property qualifies for BOFA $10,000 DOWN PAYMENT GRANT PROGAM PLUS $7500 for closing costs. Ask your agent..  Absolutely nothing to do but move in and enjoy. New roof, all new plumbing from main line to all interior pipes. New electrical from meter to panel to outlets. Updated can lighting throughout. New LVT Flooring throughout, no carpet. 4 bedrooms with a flex room for large master with built ins or great office or study space. Laundry room has nice cabinets & a counter for folding.  Excellent outdoor spaces from large patio for dinner parties accessed conveniently from the kitchen and a cozy deck out the back for morning coffee.  New Fencing all around, ready for your furry friends. Easy access to groceries, bus stops, Max station and freeways. Clackamas County taxes and North Clackamas School District make this one a must see!!
